&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Chef Daniel Patterson is the creative genius behind the Modern California cuisine at Coi, placing #75 on the 2015 World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants list, holding 2 Michelin stars, earning a place on the Gayot Top 40 Restaurants in the U.S. and being amongst the Elite Traveller Magazine&rsquo;s Elite 100. Located in the North Beach section of San Francisco, the ambiance is warmly Zen-like with calming colors and natural finishes. The format is a deeply innovative tasting menu that changes nightly. Attire is business casual. Coi offers valet parking from Thursday to Saturday for $20 via the Vatler app. Download the app by visiting bit.ly/vatlerApp and enter the code &lsquo;COI&rsquo; for $10 off your first use.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at the Coi&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://tickets.coirestaurant.com/slots/find&quot;&gt;website&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
Contact Coi by phone at +1-415-393-9000 or email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@coirestaurant.com&quot;&gt;info@coirestaurant.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coi requires purchase of tickets at the time of booking. Each ticket will include the 12 course (approximate) tasting menu per guest for $195. An additional 20% service charge and tax will also be charged at the time of booking. Wine parings may be added to the ticket price or be purchased at the time of dining and will be charged at the conclusion of the meal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can exchange your tickets up to 48 hours before your reservation date for any available tickets. Any increase in charges will be applied to your card. The restaurant is unable to refund any difference in cost of tickets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: Once a ticket is purchased there are no refunds. Tickets can be transferred to other guests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: The restaurant will contact guests by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm and discuss any dietary needs. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tickets are NON-REFUNDABLE but can be exchanged or transferred to another party through the ticketing system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

